snippet.title: Spooky Ghosts Dot Com Trailer
snippet.description:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/820620/Spooky_Ghosts_Dot_Com/

https://zertuk.itch.io/spooky-ghosts-dot-com

Ruby the ghost hunter has a tough gig this Halloween. Explore the haunted mansion, take down some ghosts, battle spooky bosses, and rescue the lost cats! 

Available on Steam and Itch August 2018!
